&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Agoda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Agoda, we bridge the world through travel. Our story began in 2005, when two lifelong friends and entrepreneurs, driven by their passion for travel, launched Agoda to make it easier for everyone to explore the world.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, we are part of Booking Holdings [NASDAQ: BKNG], with a diverse team of over 7,000 people from 90 countries, working together in offices around the globe. Every day, we connect people to destinations and experiences, with our great deals across our millions of hotels and holiday properties, flights, and experiences worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No two days are the same at Agoda. Data and technology are at the heart of our culture, fueling our curiosity and innovation. If you’re ready to begin your best journey and help build travel for the world, join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get To Know Our Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strategic Partnerships is a team of creative entrepreneurs that develop solutions for Agoda and other Booking Holdings brands’ partners and promote our top and bottom-line growth. We design tailored business and product solutions with our partners and help them generate measurable value. Members of our team are empowered and supported to grow their market(s) or accounts. We develop win-win relationships and leverage both Agoda and Booking Holdings’ unique travel product portfolio and tech solutions to bring our partners the advantages they seek. Utilizing our strong brand and resources, we build new channels to increase the visibility of Agoda and the other group companies, introducing more travelers to our great products and services and delivering significant revenues to the overall business.   &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic and results‑driven &lt;strong&gt;Senior Area Manager/Associate Director &lt;/strong&gt;with our Strategic Partnerships team to lead business development and drive revenue growth through high‑impact partnerships across South Korea and APAC market. This role is key to expanding the market presence of Agoda, Booking.com, and other Booking Holdings brands by identifying, securing, and managing strategic collaborations across sectors such as banks, airlines, loyalty programs, affiliates, and e‑commerce platforms.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead the&amp;nbsp;end‑to‑end&amp;nbsp;partnership process, from opportunity identification and stakeholder engagement to commercial negotiation and execution, while working&amp;nbsp;cross‑functionally&amp;nbsp;with product, tech, and operations teams to deliver scalable solutions. Success will be defined by your ability to unlock new revenue streams, enter new verticals, and drive profitability across key Asian markets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive New Partner Acquisition: Identify and close&amp;nbsp;high‑value&amp;nbsp;partnerships to expand travel booking distribution and brand exposure across Asia (banks, wallets/fintech, airlines/affiliates/MSE, white label/API distribution). &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Business Development:&amp;nbsp;Proactively prospect, qualify, and engage new partners via outbound, networking, and market insights; build a repeatable pipeline with clear stage gates. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Commercial Strategy:&amp;nbsp;Develop/refine partnership models and business cases (pricing, incentives, attribution, ROI, scalability), aligned to BHI&amp;nbsp;multi‑brand objectives. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
