&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Agoda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Agoda, we bridge the world through travel. Our story began in 2005, when two lifelong friends and entrepreneurs, driven by their passion for travel, launched Agoda to make it easier for everyone to explore the world.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
