&lt;p&gt;Agoda Homes—a core business line within Agoda—supports a wide range of non-hotel accommodation types including serviced apartments, homes, private villas, farm stays, chalets, boats, and more. While these accommodations have always been available on Agoda.com, today’s evolving landscape demands a sharpened focus on expanding supply and elevating quality.&amp;nbsp;Our team builds long-term, cross-cultural partnerships that create exceptional value for Agoda, our partners, and our customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As&amp;nbsp;an &lt;strong&gt;Account&amp;nbsp;Executive&lt;/strong&gt; your key&amp;nbsp;objective&amp;nbsp;is growing the coverage and quality of Agoda’s supply network. Along with your team, you take care of a&amp;nbsp;mixed&amp;nbsp;portfolio&amp;nbsp;of newly onboarded&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;high growth supply partners and&amp;nbsp;assist&amp;nbsp;in partnership related functions at scale. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proactively contact and educate&amp;nbsp;supply partners to highlight revenue growth opportunities and maximize value &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Train&amp;nbsp;supply&amp;nbsp;partners on our technologies,&amp;nbsp;tools&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;systems &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Communicate efficiently with partners through various communication methods including phone, email,&amp;nbsp;messaging&amp;nbsp;and webinars &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Encourage program participation through focused project sprints &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use data and dashboards to prioritize tasks  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prioritize daily tasks,&amp;nbsp;monitor&amp;nbsp;results&amp;nbsp;and track progress&amp;nbsp;via&amp;nbsp;internal systems &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Respond to partners requests in&amp;nbsp;a timely&amp;nbsp;and effective manner  &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minimum&amp;nbsp;2&amp;nbsp;years’ experience working in business development or execution-based&amp;nbsp;role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mid-level negotiation&amp;nbsp;and/or business development skills&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong communication&amp;nbsp;and interpersonal skills,&amp;nbsp;being able to connect and build strong rapport with partners, while also moving fast&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to work in a highly dynamic environment and&amp;nbsp;be&amp;nbsp;open to change in responsibilities&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;workflows

